data.description: Welcome to an exciting investment opportunity in Boca Raton ready for a savvy investor to unleash its full potential. Great location close to the Brightline train station, I-95, FAU, college, and beaches, rentals in this area consistently ensure a steady stream of income for the right investor.Main house, originally 3 bed, 2 bath with a garage. The garage has been converted into an extra room/storage  that can easily be restored to its original state.  What sets this property apart is the option to purchase it separately or in conjunction with two adjacent properties also available for sale. 6080 and 6060 N Dixie Highway, a world of opportunities for the right investor to build a substantial income portfolio.
